      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>The Halliday Brief | Vol. 1, No. 1 | March 21, 2026</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400&family=Source+Serif+4:ital,opsz,wght@0,8..60,300;0,8..60,400;0,8..60,600;1,8..60,300;1,8..60,400&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --ink: #2a1505;
    --soil: #1a3a1f;
    --wheat: #c9a227;
    --wheat-light: #f0d878;
    --cream: #faf8f2;
    --off-white: #f0ede3;
    --muted: #7a4e28;
    --red: #8b2020;
    --blue: #c9a227;
    --green: #e8c840;
  }

  body {
    background: #2a1f10;
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
    color: #2a1505;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 40px 16px;
  }

  .page-wrapper {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--cream);
    border: 1px solid #a08050;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 60px rgba(20,10,0,0.55), 0 0 0 6px #faf8f2, 0 0 0 7px #8a6040;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     MASTHEAD
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .masthead {
    background: #1a3a1f;
    padding: 52px 56px 36px;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 5px solid #c9a227;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .masthead::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      -45deg, transparent, transparent 22px,
      rgba(201,162,39,0.07) 22px, rgba(201,162,39,0.07) 44px
    );
  }
  .masthead-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c9a227;
    opacity: 1;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .masthead-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 76px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--cream);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.0;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .masthead-title em { font-style: italic; color: #e8c840; }
  .masthead-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: #c4a882;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    position: relative;
  }
  .masthead-rule {
    width: 72px; height: 2px;
    background: #c9a227;
    margin: 0 auto 22px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .masthead-meta {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    color: #a08060;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    position: relative;
  }
  .masthead-meta span { text-transform: uppercase; }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     THIS WEEK BAND
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .this-week {
    background: #1a3a1f;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,162,39,0.3);
    border-bottom: 4px solid #c9a227;
    padding: 28px 56px 30px;
  }
  .this-week-header {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c9a227;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .this-week-items {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 11px;
  }
  .this-week-items li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 14px;
  }
  .this-week-bullet {
    color: #e8c840;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .this-week-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--cream);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .this-week-text em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #f0d878;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     CONTENT AREA
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .content { padding: 48px 56px; }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     FROM THE DESK
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .from-desk {
    border-left: 4px solid #c9a227;
    padding: 6px 0 6px 26px;
    margin-bottom: 52px;
  }
  .from-desk-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #7a4e28;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .from-desk p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.82;
    color: var(--soil);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .from-desk p + p { margin-top: 14px; }
  .from-desk .sig {
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #2a1505;
    margin-top: 18px;
    display: block;
  }
  .from-desk .sig small {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #7a4e28;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 3px;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     SECTION HEADERS
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .section-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    margin-top: 52px;
  }
  .section-header:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .section-tag {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: #1a3a1f;
    color: #e8c840;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .section-rule {
    flex: 1; height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, #c9a227, transparent);
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     STORY CARDS
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .story {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed #c4a882;
  }
  .story:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
  .story-kicker {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--red);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .story h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.22;
    color: var(--soil);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .story .deck {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #7a4e28;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .story p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.88;
    color: #2a1505;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .story p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     RHTP FUNDING VISUAL (SVG chart)
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .chart-container {
    background: var(--off-white);
    border: 1px solid #c4a882;
    padding: 28px 28px 20px;
    margin: 28px 0;
  }
  .chart-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--soil);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .chart-sub {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #7a4e28;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .chart-svg { width: 100%; overflow: hidden; display: block; }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     NUMBERS ROW
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .numbers-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: #7a4e28;
    border: 1px solid #a08050;
    margin: 28px 0;
  }
  .number-cell {
    background: var(--off-white);
    padding: 24px 18px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .number-cell .num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--soil);
    line-height: 1;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .number-cell .num-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #7a4e28;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     DEADLINE BOX
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .deadline-box {
    background: #1a3a1f;
    color: var(--cream);
    padding: 26px 32px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .deadline-box::before {
    content: '⚑';
    position: absolute;
    top: 20px; right: 24px;
    color: #c9a227;
    font-size: 28px;
  }
  .deadline-box-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c9a227;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .deadline-box h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .deadline-box p {
    font-size: 15px !important;
    line-height: 1.75 !important;
    color: #f0d878 !important;
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }
  .deadline-date {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    background: #c9a227;
    color: #1a3a1f;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     PULLQUOTE
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .pullquote {
    border-top: 3px solid #c9a227;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #c9a227;
    padding: 26px 0;
    margin: 32px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .pullquote p {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 24px !important;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--soil) !important;
    margin-bottom: 12px !important;
  }
  .pullquote cite {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #7a4e28;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     INTEL BOX
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .intel-box {
    background: #eaf2e8;
    border-left: 5px solid #2d5a34;
    padding: 22px 28px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .intel-box-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #2d5a34;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .intel-box p {
    font-size: 15px !important;
    line-height: 1.78 !important;
    color: #2a1505 !important;
    margin-bottom: 0 !important;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     MEDICAID BAR CHART
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .bar-chart { margin: 28px 0; }
  .bar-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .bar-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #2a1505;
    width: 140px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .bar-track {
    flex: 1;
    background: #e8e0d0;
    height: 32px;
    position: relative;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }
  .bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 2px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    padding-right: 10px;
    transition: width 0.3s;
  }
  .bar-fill span {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .bar-fill.high { background: var(--red); }
  .bar-fill.mid  { background: #b05a20; }
  .bar-fill.low  { background: #c9a227; }
  .bar-fill.base { background: var(--muted); }
  .chart-legend {
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    margin-top: 10px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #7a4e28;
  }
  .legend-dot {
    width: 12px; height: 12px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     WHAT TO WATCH LIST
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .watch-list { list-style: none; margin: 0; }
  .watch-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    padding: 18px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed #c4a882;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .watch-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .watch-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #2d5a34;
    line-height: 1;
    min-width: 36px;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .watch-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #2a1505;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }
  .watch-text strong {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    display: block;
    color: var(--soil);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     TIMELINE GRAPHIC
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .timeline {
    margin: 28px 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .timeline-track {
    height: 4px;
    background: #c4a882;
    position: relative;
    margin: 32px 0 56px;
  }
  .timeline-progress {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0;
    background: #c9a227;
    width: 12%;
  }
  .timeline-nodes {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: 0; right: 0;
  }
  .t-node {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .t-dot {
    width: 24px; height: 24px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid var(--cream);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px #d0c4a8;
    background: #c4a882;
    z-index: 2;
  }
  .t-dot.active {
    background: #c9a227;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--wheat);
  }
  .t-dot.urgent {
    background: var(--red);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--red);
  }
  .t-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: 30px;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-align: center;
    color: #7a4e28;
    width: 80px;
    transform: translateX(-28px);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .t-label.urgent { color: var(--red); font-weight: 700; }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     ORNAMENT DIVIDERS
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .ornament {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 44px 0;
  }
  .ornament-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: #c4a882; }
  .ornament-symbol { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px; color: #2d5a34; }

  /* ══════════════════════════════
     FOOTER
  ══════════════════════════════ */
  .footer {
    background: #1a3a1f;
    padding: 40px 56px;
    border-top: 5px solid #c9a227;
  }
  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .footer-col-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c9a227;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .footer-col p, .footer-col a {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #c4a882;
    line-height: 1.82;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .footer-col a:hover { color: #f0d878; }
  .footer-bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid #2d5a34;
    padding-top: 22px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .footer-brand {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  .footer-brand em { color: #c9a227; font-style: italic; }
  .footer-fine {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: #7a4e28;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .masthead { padding: 36px 28px 28px; }
    .masthead-title { font-size: 52px; }
    .content { padding: 36px 28px; }
    .intro-band { padding: 14px 28px; }
    .numbers-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .footer { padding: 28px; }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
    .bar-label { width: 100px; font-size: 10px; }
    .story h2 { font-size: 25px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page-wrapper">

  <!-- ══ MASTHEAD ══ -->
  <header class="masthead">
    <div class="masthead-eyebrow">Von Halliday Consulting &nbsp;·&nbsp; North Dakota Rural Health Intelligence</div>
    <div class="masthead-title">The <em>Halliday</em> Brief</div>
    <div class="masthead-subtitle">Rural Health Policy · North Dakota &amp; Federal</div>
    <div class="masthead-rule"></div>
    <div class="masthead-meta">
      <span>Vol. 1 · No. 1</span>
      <span>March 21, 2026</span>
      <span>Inaugural Edition</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ══ THIS WEEK ══ -->
  <div class="this-week">
    <div class="this-week-header">This Week</div>
    <ul class="this-week-items">
      <li>
        <span class="this-week-bullet">◆</span>
        <span class="this-week-text">RHTP workforce grant window is open — <em>April 30 deadline</em></span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="this-week-bullet">◆</span>
        <span class="this-week-text">ND HHS statewide stakeholder call — <em>March 30</em></span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="this-week-bullet">◆</span>
        <span class="this-week-text">Medicaid work requirements: guidance still pending, <em>exposure is real</em></span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="this-week-bullet">◆</span>
        <span class="this-week-text">Nursing facility rates up 3.2% — <em>ND PDPM takes effect</em></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ CONTENT ══ -->
  <main class="content">

    <!-- FROM THE DESK -->
    <div class="from-desk">
      <div class="from-desk-label">From the Desk</div>
      <p>Welcome to the inaugural issue of <em>The Halliday Brief</em> — a weekly dispatch on the policies, funding cycles, and political currents shaping rural health in North Dakota. If you work for a critical access hospital, a tribal health program, a rural clinic network, or a health-focused foundation, this letter is written for you.</p>
      <p>This is an extraordinary moment. The first RHTP grant window just opened. The Medicaid landscape is shifting. The clock is ticking. We'll keep you oriented — every week.</p>
      <span class="sig">Doson<small>Founder, Von Halliday Consulting · Bismarck</small></span>
    </div>

    <!-- ════════════════════════════
         SECTION 1 · FEDERAL POLICY
    ═════════════════════════════ -->
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-tag">Federal Policy</div>
      <div class="section-rule"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- STORY 1 -->
    <article class="story">
      <div class="story-kicker">Breaking · RHTP Year One</div>
      <h2>The Spigot Opens: ND's First $10M Workforce Grant Window Is Live</h2>
      <p class="deck">North Dakota's 37 critical access hospitals now have until April 30 to apply for the first wave of Rural Health Transformation Program funding — targeting workforce retention and stability.</p>

      <!-- STAT TRIO -->
      <div class="numbers-row">
        <div class="number-cell"><span class="num">$199M</span><span class="num-label">ND Year One award</span></div>
        <div class="number-cell"><span class="num">$10M</span><span class="num-label">Round 1 available now</span></div>
        <div class="number-cell"><span class="num">37</span><span class="num-label">Eligible CAH grantees</span></div>
      </div>

      <p>After months of legislative maneuvering, federal review, and stakeholder meetings across the state — from Bismarck to Rugby's Cobblestone Inn — the money is finally moving. The North Dakota Department of Health and Human Services announced this week that the first RHTP funding opportunity is now open to the state's 37 critical access hospitals and their owned and operated clinics.</p>

      <p>The initial tranche targets workforce retention: an estimated 37 grants averaging $270,000 each, though CAHs may request larger amounts. Eligible uses include retention bonuses, tuition reimbursement, child care partnerships, gym memberships, professional development, and mentorship programs.</p>

